- The extension's API access path has been updated.

- Update the version number from 1.0.0.1 to 1.1.0.1.

- The sharer's name is shared and displayed correctly in the Popup.
- Able to share both HTTP and HTTPS URLs.

- Remove an unexpected character below the "Group" text on the Popup.
